    "Thus, we want to study if (or to what extent) the models' failure of reasoning is because of the shortcuts in candidate answers.",
    "We call this probe as multimodal reasoning because such short-cuts dispense with the reasoning between videos and questions, leading to a direct jump to the answers.",
